QuestData.Title: Deep Sea Venture
QuestData.Description:
As mighty as Ai'twen is, this Venture Company is still a threat to him. I need you to watch over Ai'twen and Toki as you continue your great adventure.
Eliminate the Venture Company Seawrenches that lurk the waters you travel to.
QuestData.CompletionText: Hurry to it, Ai'twen's saftey is important.
QuestData.RewardText: You've struck a mighty blow against these Venture Company thugs, and kept Ai'twen safe.
